{"tid":1471354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國放核彈去炸日本，係咪好殘暴，輸哂輿輪","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:50:00.000Z","uid":5843,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d6996b1bd5e19b87a794753724332ea831db72c0","tid":1471354,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"但大家都知，係日本先偷襲珍珠港殺人先，先撩者賤。中國先犯香港，咁香港做咩都係自衛，係你地意志力唔夠先會係度檢討受害者，一係就存心吹散水的體制中人囉。<br />\n<br />\n呢場已經唔係普通社會運動，大家要贏，就要一齊繼續意志堅定屌落去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aa48e618e2f7f6fce7787c0c90b33dc464d53514","tid":1471354,"uid":135445,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"睇住班狗係咁用琴晚攻擊我地<br />\n同時成個連登又屌鳩前線<br />\n自己同一陣線可唔可以槍口對外先呀?<br />\n核彈都唔割邊個講架?"},{"pid":"1ffc8d255ebe0cc40b98f1eb133da5c62bb5b090","tid":1471354,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"誰大誰惡誰正確"},{"pid":"1b083d1000db0371bf263ff3ddc4207a1eea33cf","tid":1471354,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa48e618e2f7f6fce7787c0c90b33dc464d53514","tid":1471354,"uid":135445,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"睇住班狗係咁用琴晚攻擊我地<br />\n同時成個連登又屌鳩前線<br />\n自己同一陣線可唔可以槍口對外先呀?<br />\n核彈都唔割邊個講架?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc3eddc93062b3f9425edc7b47d02fcf81af4d5","tid":1471354,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"果時炸完都冇人知點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae2345650879249903b7c5cbe7241d52f7bddd9","tid":1471354,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ffc8d255ebe0cc40b98f1eb133da5c62bb5b090","tid":1471354,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl